<div class='function'><span class='function_name'><a class='anchor' id='image_button.__init__'>image_button</a>.<b>__init__(form, path=None, adjust=True, frame=False, image_id=None, var=None)</b></span><div class='details'>
Constructor<br />
<br />
<span class='keyword'>Arguments:</span>
<br />
<span class='variable'>form</span> &rarr; the parent form
<br />
<br />
<span class='keyword'>Keyword arguments:</span>
<br />
<span class='variable'>path</span> &rarr; the full path to the image (default=None)
<br />
<span class='variable'>adjust</span> &rarr; indicates whether the image should be scaled according to the
<br />
size of the widget (default=True)<br />
<span class='variable'>frame</span> &rarr; indicates whether a frame should be drawn around the widget
<br />
(default=False)<br />
<span class='variable'>image_id</span> &rarr; an id to identify the image when it is clicked. If None, the
<br />
path to the image is used as id (default=None)<br />
<span class='variable'>var</span> &rarr; the name of the experimental variable that should be used to log
<br />
the widget status (default=None)<br />
</div></div>
<div class='function'><span class='function_name'><a class='anchor' id='image_button.draw_frame'>image_button</a>.<b>draw_frame(rect=None, style='normal')</b></span><div class='details'>
<i>Inherited from <b>widget</b></i><br /><br />Draws a simple frame around the widget<br />
<br />
<span class='keyword'>Keyword arguments:</span>
<br />
<span class='variable'>rect</span> &rarr; a (left, top, width, height) tuple for the frame geometry or
<br />
None to use the widget geometry (default=None)<br />
<span class='variable'>style</span> &rarr; 'normal', 'active', 'light' (default='normal')
<br />
</div></div>
<div class='function'><span class='function_name'><a class='anchor' id='image_button.on_mouse_click'>image_button</a>.<b>on_mouse_click(pos)</b></span><div class='details'>
Is called whenever the user clicks on the widget. Returns the image_id<br />
or the path to the image if no image_id has been specified.<br />
<br />
<span class='keyword'>Arguments:</span>
<br />
<span class='variable'>pos</span> &rarr; an (x, y) tuple
<br />
</div></div>
